resources.string:
To make Android ignore the midsession, please try one of these options:

1) Disable mobile data while using Wi-Fi;

2) Tap on the "Sign in to Wi-Fi network" notification and choose "Use this network as is" in the menu bar;

3) Enable "Fix system-wide check" in preferences (requires root or a PC, but needs to be done only once);

4) Enable "Handle midsession" in preferences (might not work depending on the internet provider).
